{"type":"message","id":"7fae3cae","parentId":"fc8d262e","timestamp":"2026-04-01T03:00:59.335Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"从 `crontab -l` 的输出来看，你目前只设置了 **1个** 定时任务：\n\n```cron\n# OpenClaw 每日资讯推送 - 每天上午8点执行\n0 8 * * * /Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/openclaw_daily_push.sh\n```\n\n就是每天早上 8 点创建每日资讯任务文件，没有其他 crontab 任务了。\n\n你之前说的\"热饭\"，是不是我理解错了？还有别的任务我没找到吗？😂"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-ark-cn-beijing-volces-com","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":14501,"output":124,"cacheRead":4920,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":19545,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775012452712,"responseId":"02177501245287155eca07af4019b515b4a7e2058cdd06738f73f"}}
